               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsān maḥyawi “The Life-Giving Homily” (fols. 3ra-72ra)&#xD; I-1)
                     Introductory prayer (fol. 3ra-va) &#xD; I-2) Reading for Monday, Compline
                     (nǝwam) (fols. 3va-15rb) &#xD; I-3) Reading for Tuesday, Matins (manfaqa lelit)
                     (fols. 15va-25va) &#xD; I-4) Reading for Wednesday, Lauds (nagh) (fols.
                     25vb-35rb) &#xD; I-5) Reading for Thursday, Terce (śalastu säʿat) (fols.
                     35va-46vb) &#xD; I-6) Reading for Friday, Sext (qätr) (fols. 47ra-55vb) &#xD;
                     I-7) Reading for Saturday, None (täsaʿtu säʿat) (fols. 55vb-65va) &#xD; I-8)
                     Reading for Sunday, Vespers (śark) (fols. 65va-72ra) &#xD; II) Malkǝʾa ʾIyasus
                     “Image of Jesus” (fols. 72ra-76rb) (s. ChRep no. 125)&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1;
                     colophon.</summary>
